OL,3,CSuper-fit spinner set to break world
OL,4,Crecord by pedalling for 280 hours
OL,6,FIf you've got your mind set on getting
OL,7,Fin shape this New Year then you can
OL,8,Ftake inspiration from one man from
OL,9,FWeston-super-Mare, who is aiming to
OL,10,Fbreak the world record for the longest
OL,11,Ftime spent pedalling on an exercise
OL,12,Fbike.
OL,14,FPaul Magor is set to break the record
OL,15,Fon Sunday 12 January, after clocking
OL,16,Fup a remarkable 280 hours at his local
OL,17,Fgym in Worle. The current world record
OL,18,Ffor the longest time spent on a spin
OL,19,Fbike is 227 hours.
