OL,3,CSuper-fit spinner set to break world
OL,4,Crecord by pedalling for 280 hours
OL,6,FIn the process Paul's aiming to raise
OL,7,Ftens of thousands of pounds for Weston
OL,8,FHospicecare.
OL,10,FHis record-breaking bid comes with
OL,11,Fstrict rules: he has to eat and drink
OL,12,Fand wash while on the bike, and pedal
OL,13,Fthe equivalent of 20 kilometres - or
OL,14,F12 miles - every hour. Paul can take a
OL,15,Ffive-minute break every hour, but can
OL,16,Fbank those five minutes if he pedals
OL,17,Fcontinuously through several hours.
OL,19,FCurrently he's on course to break the
OL,20,Frecord late on Sunday 12 January.
