OL,6,FThe event is taking place around the
OL,7,Fclock at the Worle Centre, the
OL,8,Fcommunity-run sports centre and gym.
OL,9,FPaul is being accompanied by regular
OL,10,Fspin bike classes that take place
OL,11,Fthere.
OL,13,FPaul said: "This is a huge challenge
OL,14,Fand I have spent months trying to
OL,15,Fprepare my body for what it is going
OL,16,Fthrough.
