OL,3,CSuper-fit spinner set to break world
OL,4,Crecord by pedalling for 280 hours
OL,6,F"My legs are aching from the constant
OL,7,Fstrain, but I have been blessed to
OL,8,Fhave a lot of lovely visitors,
OL,9,Fsupporters and witnesses come in to
OL,10,Fsupport me and cheer me on.
OL,12,F"There is still a long road ahead but
OL,13,FI am determined to complete this
OL,14,Fchallenge all while raising money for
OL,15,Fa worthy cause, Weston Hospicecare."
