OL,3,CSuper-fit spinner set to break world
OL,4,Crecord by pedalling for 280 hours
OL,6,FIf he completes 280 hours while riding
OL,7,Fat an average of 20kph, he'll have
OL,8,Fridden the equivalent of 3,300 miles -
OL,9,Froughly the distance from Worle to New
OL,10,FYork - without moving more than an
OL,11,Finch on his spin bike.
OL,13,FThe idea for the world-record breaking
OL,14,Fbid came from a record spinathon Paul
OL,15,Fcompleted with 28 others in July 2023,
OL,16,Fpedalling more than 31 hours at the
OL,17,Fgym, and raising #35,000 for the
OL,18,Fhospice.
